<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Travel information</h3>
    Bus informationThe no. 81, 82 and 88 bus departs from Doncaster town centre to Doncaster Royal Infirmary.Road informationThe Royal Infirmary is situated 1 mile from the town centre and is easily accessible due to good public transport routes and its location in the centre of the M1, M62, M18 and A1(M). <br/>Local directionThe Royal Infirmary is situated 1 mile from the town centre and is easily accessible due to good public transport routes and its location in the centre of the M1, M62, M18 and A1(M). <br/><br/><a href="http://www.dbh.nhs.uk/index.asp?hospitalname=Doncaster"> Detailed Map </a>Rail informationDoncaster Railway Station is situated on Trafford Way in the town centre opposite Frenchgate Shopping Centre.


</div>
</div>
