<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>A park &amp; ride is available opposite Doncaster Racecourse.  A shuttle service runs between our hospitals.The main entrance to DRI is at Gate 4, Armthorpe Road, where there is a Pay &amp; Display car park.</p>
